%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'fontSize':'14px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant FE as AvatarCard + useProfileAvatar (browser)
    participant API as NestJS API (JWT guard)
    participant S3 as AWS S3 (private bucket)
    participant DB as MongoDB (users)
    participant CDN as CloudFront CDN

    rect rgb(237,233,254)
    Note over U,CDN: UPLOAD a new photo
    U->>FE: choose file
    FE->>FE: validate type (jpeg/png/webp) + size (<=5MB)
    FE->>API: POST /api/me/avatar/upload-url {contentType}
    API->>API: RequestAvatarUploadOrchestrator<br/>build key avatars/userId/uuid.ext + presign PUT
    API-->>FE: {uploadUrl, key, expiresInSeconds=300}
    FE->>S3: PUT file bytes directly to presigned URL
    S3-->>FE: 200 OK
    FE->>API: PUT /api/me/avatar {key}
    API->>API: SetAvatarOrchestrator<br/>owns key? headObject exists? size+type ok?
    API->>DB: save avatarKey (read previous first)
    API->>S3: deleteObject(previousKey) if replaced
    API-->>FE: PublicUser {avatarUrl = https CDN url}
    FE->>FE: updateCurrentUser -> Redux store
    end

    rect rgb(219,234,254)
    Note over U,CDN: READ everywhere (topbar, sidebar, messages)
    U->>CDN: GET https://cdn/avatars/userId/uuid.png
    CDN->>S3: origin fetch via OAC (cache miss only)
    CDN-->>U: image, cached at edge
    end

    rect rgb(254,226,226)
    Note over U,CDN: REMOVE the photo
    U->>API: DELETE /api/me/avatar
    API->>API: RemoveAvatarOrchestrator
    API->>DB: clear avatarKey
    API->>S3: deleteObject(key)
    API-->>U: PublicUser {avatarUrl = null} -> initials fallback
    end
